  render_p(sec, "Each new prime slows the carousel. The gap shrinks but never to zero. LATTICE INVARIANCE (S489): ALL 108 lambda-420 rings share gap = 0.016. b^2 rules universally. Only adding 13^2=169 (which breaks the lattice) would narrow it further.");
