  render_p(sec, "Level 4 is special: classes = phi = 48. Seeing and acting coincide. At level 5, classes = e_2 of the shadow chain = 288. Max class size: 2^(level-1). The multiplicity structure is a perfect power-of-two staircase. Per-channel count: floor(m/2)+1. Product for TRUE FORM: 5*5*13*25*6 = 48750.");
